t: To the choirmaster. A Psalm of David. A Song.
Praise*pn is due to you, O God, in Zion, and*ld to you shall vows be performed.
O*ln you who hear prayer, to*ld you shall all flesh come.

Blessed*ln is the one you choose and bring near, to*ld dwell in your courts! We*ln shall be satisfied with the goodness of your house, the*ld holiness of your temple!
